{"tid":1345233,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"元朗單野一定要推返上政治層面","createTime":"2019-07-22T01:39:13.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-22T02:36:32.000Z","uid":302,"like":8,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"7fa725edc1669c64c46abda600bf4e3f6ced8e06","tid":1345233,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:39:13.000Z","msg":"好明顯 政府想割蓆 但都好明顯 呢單野係中聯辦操盤<br />\n由何君妖策劃 想令普通中立或偏藍既市民睇到以為係黑社會同示威者既黑白對抗 然後置身事外 再等一會收拾殘局 <br />\n元朗班勝和仔就一定要收拾 但文宣一定要先強調佢地係由西環契仔何君妖出馬 一定要將呢班人同港共政權掛勾 再加上警黑聯手 形成今日政府之醜惡<br />\n唔好比呢班鄉黑可以同港共脫到勾 無論如何 都要強調 示威者對抗極權 鄉黑同黑警只係極權下既打手機器！"},{"pid":"177eac8513d5995c36808ad9a776b558dd2b2693","tid":1345233,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:40:37.000Z","msg":"藍絲 黑警 鄉黑 政府 中共=極權<br />\n示威者=普通市民"},{"pid":"a4c0802e5321228dd5f7efa660f9c3e9faf31efd","tid":1345233,"uid":268153,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:41:33.000Z","msg":"「超重要」點解打柒何君堯好重要<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1345058\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1345058</a>"},{"pid":"848a21fc704dbe80e836e13df57987aae7b0ee64","tid":1345233,"uid":221696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:41:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2019/07/22/093123_9f7d9c7c1b682c47a5e249f59bbc821e.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2019%2F07%2F22%2F093123_9f7d9c7c1b682c47a5e249f59bbc821e.png&h=d969c48e&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"66037c26ac2990da2644c13064d55e53f379c1ac","tid":1345233,"uid":302,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:48:48.000Z","msg":"中共會想搵何君妖祭旗 但千萬唔好比中共祭到旗 點都要將何君妖同中聯辦 甚至港澳辦 掛勾！"},{"pid":"b7a348ee4eb67b13c46738beee37cdbf2a829830","tid":1345233,"uid":279167,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-22T01:50:59.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"bbeae099f788759d659d62b64c7a90e415c8fe0c","tid":1345233,"uid":302,"l